'''纓翅目'''（學名：{{lang|la|Thysanoptera}}）是[[昆虫纲|昆虫纲]]的一目，通稱为'''薊馬'''、'''刺馬'''（{{lang-nan-tw|tshì-bé}}）<ref>{{Cite news|title=乾旱助長薊馬蟲害 屏東芒果著果率差－民視台語新聞|date=2021-03-15|accessdate=2021-10-24|publisher=民視新聞網 Formosa TV News network|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ey1wdU7BbMw|archive-date=2021-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211023172423/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ey1wdU7BbMw|dead-url=no}}</ref>。舊稱'''泡足目'''（{{lang|la|Physopoda}}）<ref name="kknews">{{cite news |title=薊馬的形態特徵與分類 |date=2018-07-29 |access-date=2020-06-01 |language=zh }}</ref>，因為其足跗節具有獨特的可外翻胞狀囊<ref name="baphiq">{{cite journal |url=https://www.baphiq.gov.tw/redirect_files.php?id=17535&file_name=Iug0TZsLqZ4K8KJSDO0J0LsIDFKz7oPaEcif53Sw7gWGEqualWGEqualzfHVLWm1Y1aoqzmRbelPpu2zAxHXVWGPlusH5aCwydzWGSlash0yxTx |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |title=植物防疫檢疫重要薊馬類害蟲簡介 |author=[[張念台|張念台]] |journal=植物重要防疫檢疫害蟲診斷鑑定研習會之二 |date=2002-11 |page=35-97 |language=zh-hant |access-date=2020-06-02 |archive-date=2020-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928231730/https://www.baphiq.gov.tw/redirect_files.php?id=17535&file_name=Iug0TZsLqZ4K8KJSDO0J0LsIDFKz7oPaEcif53Sw7gWGEqualWGEqualzfHVLWm1Y1aoqzmRbelPpu2zAxHXVWGPlusH5aCwydzWGSlash0yxTx |dead-url=no }}</ref>，使之可黏附在基底上。

==形態描述==
[[File:Ponticulothrips_diospyrosi.jpg|thumb]]''。]]
本目物種小型而细长的昆蟲，體長0.5至5 mm{{r|baphiq|page1=35}}，一般黄褐或黑色；眼睛发达；[[翅膀|翅膀]]狭长，翅缘扁长，具有少数或无翅脉，不少種類的翅膀外緣有排列整齊的長細毛，所以稱為纓翅目；尾缺鬚。{{cn|time=2020-06-01|变态为[[渐进变态|渐进变态]]}}。

纓翅目物種有其獨特的左右不对称穿透性刺吸式{{r|baphiq|page1=36}}口器，通常在花朵上和花朵中發現。食性相當廣泛，當中有不少的種類是重要的[[農業|農業]][[害蟲|害蟲]]：大多數種類是食植物性的，以花或花粉為食；也有些種類以[[真菌|真菌]]為食，而少數種類是以其他昆蟲（例如：其他小型昆蟲或者[[螨類|螨類]]）為食。

==分類==
[[纓翅目|纓翅目]]（[[Thysanoptera|Thysanoptera]]）包括有5500個物種，按其[[產卵管|產卵管]]（即其第十腹節{{r|baphiq|page1=38}}）之形態再細分為兩個亞目{{r|baphiq|page1=39}}：

[[Terebrantia|錐尾亞目]]（[[Terebrantia|Terebrantia]]）的物種有[[錐狀|錐狀]]產卵管；
:{{tsl|en|Adiheterothripidae|寬錐薊馬科}} {{tsl|en|Adiheterothripidae}}
:{{tsl|en|Aeolothripidae|紋薊馬科}} {{tsl|en|Aeolothripidae}}<!-- Zootaxa 864: 1–16 (2005) -->
:{{tsl|en|Fauriellidae|斷域薊馬科}} {{tsl|en|Fauriellidae}}
:{{tsl|en|Hemithripidae|半薊馬科}} {{tsl|en|Hemithripidae}}†
:{{tsl|en|Heterothripidae|異薊馬科}} {{tsl|en|Heterothripidae}}
: [[Jezzinothripidae|Jezzinothripidae]]†
: [[Karataothripidae|Karataothripidae]]†
: [[黑薊馬亞科|黑薊馬科]] [[Melanthripidae|Melanthripidae]]：部分文獻視為[[紋薊馬科|紋薊馬科]]之下的亞科{{r|baphiq|page1=39}}；
:{{tsl|en|Merothripidae|食孢薊馬科}} {{tsl|en|Merothripidae}}
: [[Scudderothripidae|Scudderothripidae]]†
: [[Stenurothripidae|Stenurothripidae]]
:{{tsl|en|Thripidae|薊馬科}} {{tsl|en|Thripidae}}
: [[三疊紀薊馬科|三疊紀薊馬科]] [[Triassothripidae|Triassothripidae]]†{{r|kknews}}
:{{tsl|en|Uzelothripidae|膜薊馬科}} {{tsl|en|Uzelothripidae}}

{{tsl|en|Tubulifera|管尾亞目}}（{{tsl|en|Tubulifera}}）物種的腹部並沒有伸出錐狀的產卵管並不是錐狀，而是管狀的。只有[[管薊馬科|管薊馬科]]（[[Phlaeothripidae|Phlaeothripidae]]）一科，下分為[[管薊馬亞科|管薊馬亞科]]（[[Phlaeothripinae|Phlaeothripinae]]）及[[寬薊馬亞科|寬薊馬亞科]]（[[Idolothripinae|Idolothripinae]]）兩個亞科{{r|baphiq|page1=39}}。

== 社會行為 ==
許多種類的纓翅目物種會在植物上取食或產卵時形成[[癭|癭]]。一些{{link-en|管薊馬科|Phlaeothripidae}}的物種例如：''{{link-en|Kladothrips}}'' 屬<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Kranz, B.D.|author2= Schwarz, M.P.|author3= Mound, L.A.|author4= Crespi, B.J. |author-link4=Bernard Crespi|year=1999 |title=Social biology and sex ratios of the eusocial gall-inducing thrips ''Kladothrips hamiltoni'' |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_ecological-entomology_1999-11_24_4/page/432|journal=Ecological Entomology |volume=24 |issue=4 |pages=432–442 |doi=10.1046/j.1365-2311.1999.00207.x}}</ref>與''{{link-en|Oncothrips}}'' 屬<ref>{{cite journal |first1=Brenda D. |last1=Kranz |first2=Michael P. |last2=Schwarz |first3=Taryn E. |last3=Wills |first4=Thomas W. |last4=Chapman |first5=David C. |last5=Morris |first6=Bernard J. |last6=Crespi |year=2001 |title=A fully reproductive fighting morph in a soldier clade of gall-inducing thrips (''Oncothrips morrisi'') |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_behavioral-ecology-and-sociobiology_2001-07_50_2/page/151 |journal=Behavioral Ecology and Sociobiology |volume=50 |issue=2 |pages=151–161 |jstor=4601948 |doi=10.1007/s002650100347}}</ref>，在癭中形成[[真社會性|真社會性]]結構，類似於[[螞蟻|螞蟻]]，包含了具有繁殖能力的[[蟻后|-{后}-蟲]]以及沒有繁殖能力的士兵階級（相當於蟻群中的兵蟻）<ref>{{cite book |author1=Crespi, B.J. |author2=Mound, L.A. |year=1997 |chapter-url=https://books.google.co.id/books?id=qkHHO_SmM_kC&pg=PA166 |chapter=Ecology and evolution of social behaviour among Australian gall thrips and their allies |editor1=Choe, J.C. |editor2=Crespi, B.J. |title=The evolution of social behaviour of insects and arachnids |publisher=Cambridge University Press |pages=166–180 |isbn=978-0-521-58977-2 |access-date=2019-04-14 |archive-date=2019-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607031517/https://books.google.co.id/books?id=qkHHO_SmM_kC&pg=PA166 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=Chapman, T.W.|author2=Crespi, B.J. |year=1998 |title=High relatedness and inbreeding in two species of haplodiploid eusocial thrips (Insecta: Thysanoptera) revealed by microsatellite analysis |journal=Behavioral Ecology and Sociobiology |volume=43 |issue=4 |pages=301–306 |doi=10.1007/s002650050495 |jstor=4601521}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |first1=Brenda D. |last1=Kranz |first2=Michael P. |last2=Schwarz |first3=David C. |last3=Morris |first4=Bernard J. |last4=Crespi |year= 2002 |title=Life history of ''Kladothrips ellobus'' and ''Oncothrips rodwayi'': insight into the origin and loss of soldiers in gall-inducing thrips |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_ecological-entomology_2002-02_27_1/page/49 |journal=Ecological Entomology |volume=27 |issue=1 |pages=49–57 |doi=10.1046/j.1365-2311.2002.0380a.x}}</ref>。

